11 payments to qualifying counties under this section. This
12 appropriation shall not be transferred or expended for any other
13 purpose. Notwithstanding W.S. 9-2-1008, 9-2-1012(e) and 9-4-207,
14 any unexpended, unobligated funds remaining from this
15 appropriation shall not revert until June 30, 2027. It is the
16 intent of the legislature that this appropriation not be included
17 in the standard budget of the department of revenue for the
18 immediately succeeding fiscal biennium.
