20 (b) The department of revenue shall establish a grant
21 application and program for distribution of the funds appropriated
22 in subsection (a) of this section and as specified in this
23 subsection. Not more than one-half (1/2) of the amount appropriated
24 in subsection (a) of this section may be distributed for purposes
25 of restoring revenue attributable to any reduction in residential
26 property tax assessments from tax year 2025. Any remaining funds
27 from the appropriation in subsection (a) of this section shall be
28 available for distribution for purposes of restoring revenue
29 attributable to any reduction in residential property tax
30 assessments from tax year 2026.
