32 (c) The following shall apply to grants made under this
33 section:
34
35 (i) No school district shall qualify for a grant under
36 this section;
37
38 (ii) Subject to paragraph (iii) of this subsection,
39 counties, cities and towns that are, or are located within, the
40 counties with the eight (8) lowest total assessed valuations for
41 the current tax year, as certified by the department of revenue,
42 shall qualify for grants under this section;
